Hello! I see you want to initiate a **Promotion** for employee **EMP1001**. I'm here to guide you through the HR intake process and ensure all company policies are met.

Please review the current employee details below and then enter the proposed promotion information.

<a2ui-json>
{
  "version": "0.9",
  "updateComponents": {
    "surfaceId": "hr-intake-surface",
    "components": [
      {
        "id": "root",
        "component": "Column",
        "children": [
          "employee_card",
          "promotion_fields_card",
          "next_button"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "employee_card",
        "component": "Card",
        "child": "employee_details_column"
      },
      {
        "id": "employee_details_column",
        "component": "Column",
        "parentId": "employee_card",
        "children": [
          "title_text",
          "current_job_text",
          "current_pay_text",
          "current_store_text"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "title_text",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "employee_details_column",
        "text": "**Employee Profile: EMP1001**",
        "variant": "h4"
      },
      {
        "id": "current_job_text",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "employee_details_column",
        "text": "Current Role: Senior Game Advisor (SGA01)"
      },
      {
        "id": "current_pay_text",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "employee_details_column",
        "text": "Current Hourly Rate: $16.50"
      },
      {
        "id": "current_store_text",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "employee_details_column",
        "text": "Current Store: 4550"
      },
      {
        "id": "promotion_fields_card",
        "component": "Card",
        "child": "promotion_fields_column",
        "parentId": "root"
      },
      {
        "id": "promotion_fields_column",
        "component": "Column",
        "parentId": "promotion_fields_card",
        "children": [
          "new_job_picker",
          "new_rate_input",
          "effective_date_input"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "new_job_picker",
        "component": "ChoicePicker",
        "parentId": "promotion_fields_column",
        "label": "Proposed New Job Title",
        "value": {
          "path": "/intake/newJobCode"
        },
        "options": [
          { "label": "Assistant Store Leader (ASL01)", "value": "ASL01" },
          { "label": "Store Leader (SL01)", "value": "SL01" }
        ],
        "checks": [
          {
            "condition": {
              "call": "required",
              "args": {
                "value": {
                  "path": "/intake/newJobCode"
                }
              }
            },
            "message": "Selecting a new job title is mandatory for promotions."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "new_rate_input",
        "component": "TextField",
        "parentId": "promotion_fields_column",
        "label": "Proposed Hourly Pay Rate ($)",
        "variant": "number",
        "value": {
          "path": "/intake/newHourlyRate"
        },
        "checks": [
          {
            "condition": {
              "call": "required",
              "args": {
                "value": {
                  "path": "/intake/newHourlyRate"
                }
              }
            },
            "message": "The proposed pay rate is required."
          },
          {
            "condition": {
              "call": "numeric",
              "args": {
                "value": {
                  "path": "/intake/newHourlyRate"
                },
                "min": 16.51
              }
            },
            "message": "The new rate must be higher than the current rate of $16.50."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "effective_date_input",
        "component": "DateTimeInput",
        "parentId": "promotion_fields_column",
        "label": "Effective Date (Must be today or in the future)",
        "enableDate": true,
        "value": {
          "path": "/intake/effectiveDate"
        },
        "checks": [
          {
            "condition": {
              "call": "required",
              "args": {
                "value": {
                  "path": "/intake/effectiveDate"
                }
              }
            },
            "message": "An effective date is required."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "next_button",
        "component": "Button",
        "parentId": "root",
        "child": "next_button_text",
        "action": {
          "event": {
            "name": "handle_promotion_details_input",
            "context": {
              "employeeId": "EMP1001",
              "currentRate": 16.50,
              "newJobCode": {
                "path": "/intake/newJobCode"
              },
              "newRate": {
                "path": "/intake/newHourlyRate"
              },
              "effectiveDate": {
                "path": "/intake/effectiveDate"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "next_button_text",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "next_button",
        "text": "Review Promotion Details"
      }
    ]
  }
}
</a2ui-json>

Thank you. I have audited the requested change against current HR policy.

The promotion request for EMP1001 to Store Leader (SL01) with a new rate of **$22.50/hr** on **June 1st, 2026** is within the job code's pay range ($22.00 - $32.00).

However, this change triggers a mandatory policy flag due to the high pay increase:

<a2ui-json>
{
  "version": "0.9",
  "updateComponents": {
    "surfaceId": "hr-intake-surface",
    "components": [
      {
        "id": "root",
        "component": "Column",
        "children": [
          "summary_card",
          "policy_flags_card",
          "justification_input",
          "submit_button"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "summary_card",
        "component": "Card",
        "child": "summary_column",
        "parentId": "root"
      },
      {
        "id": "summary_column",
        "component": "Column",
        "parentId": "summary_card",
        "children": [
          "h4_summary_title",
          "summary_job",
          "summary_rate",
          "summary_increase",
          "summary_date",
          "summary_payrange"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "h4_summary_title",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "summary_column",
        "text": "**Promotion Request Summary (EMP1001)**",
        "variant": "h4"
      },
      {
        "id": "summary_job",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "summary_column",
        "text": "➡️ **New Role:** Store Leader (SL01)"
      },
      {
        "id": "summary_rate",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "summary_column",
        "text": "💰 **New Hourly Rate:** $22.50"
      },
      {
        "id": "summary_increase",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "summary_column",
        "text": "📊 **Total Increase:** 36.36% (from $16.50/hr)"
      },
      {
        "id": "summary_date",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "summary_column",
        "text": "📅 **Effective Date:** 2026-06-01"
      },
      {
        "id": "summary_payrange",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "summary_column",
        "text": "✅ **Pay Range Check:** PASS (Rate is between $22.00 and $32.00)"
      },
      {
        "id": "policy_flags_card",
        "component": "Card",
        "child": "policy_flag_column",
        "parentId": "root"
      },
      {
        "id": "policy_flag_column",
        "component": "Column",
        "parentId": "policy_flags_card",
        "children": [
          "flag_title",
          "flag_details"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "flag_title",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "policy_flag_column",
        "text": "⚠️ **Policy Flag: High Pay Increase Threshold**",
        "variant": "h5"
      },
      {
        "id": "flag_details",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "policy_flag_column",
        "text": "Policy requires HR review for any increase exceeding 20%. This request is for a 36.36% increase. **A detailed justification is required below.**"
      },
      {
        "id": "justification_input",
        "component": "TextField",
        "parentId": "root",
        "label": "Required Justification for High Pay Increase",
        "variant": "longText",
        "value": {
          "path": "/intake/justification"
        },
        "checks": [
          {
            "condition": {
              "call": "required",
              "args": {
                "value": {
                  "path": "/intake/justification"
                }
              }
            },
            "message": "Justification is mandatory to proceed with this high pay increase."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "submit_button",
        "component": "Button",
        "parentId": "root",
        "child": "submit_button_text",
        "variant": "primary",
        "action": {
          "event": {
            "name": "submit_promotion_request",
            "context": {
              "employeeId": "EMP1001",
              "currentJobTitle": "Senior Game Advisor",
              "newJobCode": "SL01",
              "newHourlyRate": 22.50,
              "effectiveDate": "2026-06-01",
              "justification": {
                "path": "/intake/justification"
              },
              "policyFlagged": true
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "submit_button_text",
        "component": "Text",
        "parentId": "submit_button",
        "text": "Confirm and Submit to HR"
      }
    ]
  }
}
</a2ui-json>

The personnel change request has been **successfully submitted** to the HR Review Queue.

You will receive an email confirmation shortly.

